flowchart LR
    Browser[UI Browser<br/>:5173] -->|GET /asset-graph| Vite[Vite Proxy]
    Browser -->|GET /threats/graph| Vite
    Vite --> API[FastAPI<br/>:8080]
    API --> Auth[JWT require_auth]
    Auth --> AssetEP[GET /api/v1/asset-graph]
    Auth --> AttackEP[GET /api/v1/attack-paths]
    AssetEP --> Session[AsyncSession via get_session]
    AttackEP --> Session
    Session --> AG[(asset_graph)]
    Session --> AP[(attack_paths)]
    Session --> AL[(audit_log)]
    AG --> AssetResp[AssetGraphResponse]
    AP --> AttackResp[AttackPathsResponse]
    AL --> AssetResp
    AssetResp --> Browser
    AttackResp --> Browser
    Browser --> D3A[D3 force graph]
    Browser --> D3B[D3 layered graph]
    D3A --> RenderA[SVG render]
    D3B --> RenderB[SVG render]
    Session -->|pool/session error| ApiErr[NRVQ-API-7050-ERR / 7051-ERR]
